on base of vm2(module1) create new virtual mashine
add here new virtual hdd
start this vm
install ntfs packages(yum install ntfs-3g)
create ntfs drive (fdisk)
create folder /mnt/ntfs
mount ntfs drive to this folder(/etc/fstab)
add user toor
set toor as owner for /mnt/ntfs
install git
create clone of project my "homework"
instal components of nfs-server and start them
add new rule to firewall
share folder (/etc/export)
